name: The first person to ever love me
description:
#Herbie7777777

--------------
She's honest, of integrity, funny, a bit crazy. Enjoys life as much as possible. 
She's an amazing artist. Easygoing. Can talk about literally everything. Doesn't take herself too seriously. Had a fucking tough childhood and made it through quite sane. She always does her best and tries to give us what we need.
Thank you for everything.
I love you, Mom. You're the best.
